    dc:creator "Megna, Yoandri S.; Balke, Michael; Apenborn, Rico; Hendrich, Lars" ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "A review of Peruvian diving beetles of the genus Hydaticus Leach, 1817, with description of Hydaticus (Prodaticus) panguana sp. nov. and notes on other Neotropical species (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3995400>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3995402>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3995404> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3995400>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dorsal view of the colour pattern of a generalized Hydaticus for the Neotropical region. Head (He): Ptbb-posterior transverse black band. Pronotum (Pr): Abb- anterior black band; Pbb-posterior black band; Plaa- posterior lateral angle acute. Scutellum (Sc). Elytron (El): Ai- apex irrorated; Bs- basal spot; Ls- lateral yellow stripes; Ms- middle spot; Sls- Subbasal and lateral yellow stripe; Tbf- transverse basal fasciae; Tpi- third posterior irrorated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3995400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3995402>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal habitus of H. panguana sp. nov. (A), H. lateralis (B), H. subfasciatus (C) and H. xanthomelas (D). All specimens collected in Panguana, Peru. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3995402/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3995404>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsal habitus of H. fractivittis (A) and H. palliatus (B), both from Paraguay, and H. rimosus (C) from Guatemala. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3995404/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

